@startuml 2FA Setup Flow
!theme plain
title Two-Factor Authentication Setup

actor User
participant "Frontend" as FE
participant "AuthController" as AC
participant "TwoFAService" as TFA
participant "JWTService" as JWT
participant "Database" as DB

== 2FA Setup ==
User -> FE: Enable 2FA
FE -> AC: POST /auth/2fa/setup
AC -> JWT: verify(token from cookie)
JWT --> AC: {email, provider, twoFA}
AC -> TFA: setup(token)
TFA -> JWT: verify(token)
JWT --> TFA: {email}
TFA -> TFA: generate(email) - speakeasy.generateSecret()
TFA -> TFA: qrcode.toDataURL()
TFA -> DB: User.update({twoFASecret})
DB --> TFA: success
TFA --> AC: {qrImageUrl, otpauth_url}
AC --> FE: QR code and setup URL
FE --> User: Display QR code for authenticator app

note right of TFA: Generates secret with speakeasy\nCreates QR code for auth app\nStores secret in database

@enduml
